review_content: The processor is really good for people with lga1155 motherboards, who are looking to buy a graphics card for 1080p gaming. It will save your cost for motherboard, which you can use on your graphics card as well as provides enough punch with 4 cores to your system to run AAA games. One of the main disadvantage is that it does not come with hyperthreading which is available at i7 3770 but it costs double the money.
